DETAILED BREAKDOWN: KEY CONCEPTS

Template Level Reality

• There is a template level of reality
• This is more non-physical than physical reality
• Cannabis vibrates at the frequency just below this template level
• This makes cannabis a gateway between:
  - Physical reality
  - Template level reality
• Allowing flexibility, plasticity, and malleability of physical reality

Natural Plant Teachers

• Anything growing naturally from the earth can be a teacher and guide
• They teach by instilling a specific vibration/frequency in you
• The point is to learn that frequency so you can generate it yourself
• Generating it yourself without the substance is a HIGHER FORM of that energy

The Excitement vs. Anxiety Test

**Choosing from Excitement:**
- Feels expansive, light, natural
- No emptiness afterward
- Holistic, includes all parts of yourself
- Creates genuine fulfillment

**Choosing from Anxiety:**
- Glosses over deeper issues
- Goes into denial
- Creates emptiness
- Attempts to fill hole from outside
- Dulls senses to avoid facing anxiety
- Is not truly excitement, just labeled as such

The Fear Structure

1. Experience anxiety
2. Afraid to investigate why anxious
3. Avoid investigation by choosing something and calling it "excitement"
4. Fear beneath: "What if the negative belief is actually true?"
5. The negative beliefs: lack of self-worth, lack of self-esteem, non-deservability
6. These are often fed to people as children

The Truth Structure

1. Your existence is proof of your deservability
2. Creation doesn't make mistakes
3. If you were truly unworthy, you wouldn't exist
4. All that is needs you to be all that is
5. You are important, valuable, necessary to creation
6. There are no superfluous creations
7. Any belief in unworthiness is just a belief/definition
8. It can never be empirically, fundamentally true

